query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 1 AND q.favorite_count <= 10
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('physics')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('black-holes',
'classical-mechanics',
'condensed-matter',
'cosmology',
'electromagnetism',
'electrostatics',
'fluid-dynamics',
'forces',
'newtonian-mechanics',
'optics',
'particle-physics',
'quantum-mechanics',
'special-relativity',
'thermodynamics');
